## **Python Library for talking to Atmos MGMT API**

This API allows Python developers to easily connect to EMC Atmos mgmt services. It handles all of the low-level tasks such as generating and signing requests, connecting to the server, and parsing server responses.

## **Requirements**

* Python 2.7

## **Usage**

In order to use the library, you need to construct an instance of the specified class. This class contains the parameters used to connect to the server.

eg.

stid = subtenant.Subtenant(tenantname='Tenant', tenantadmin='Atmin1', tenantadminpassword='Password', endpoint='[http://youratmoshere](http://youratmoshere)')

